Report Illegal/Unethical Conduct
HGST is committed to principles of business ethics and lawful conduct in all of its business operations.
If you become aware of any unlawful or unethical situation involving HGST, including unethical or inappropriate conduct; conduct that violates the law; conduct that involves improper accounting practices and/or false or misleading financial reporting; conduct that violates HGST corporate instructions, policies or procedures; and/or hazardous or unsafe working conditions, please inform us immediately.
You may report any suspected unlawful or unethical situation using HGST's Ethics Hotline.  To contact the Ethics Hotline by phone, dial 1-877-548-6716.  To make a report via the web, access the web-based Ethics Hotline reporting system at: https://wdc.alertline.com.
You may report your concerns anonymously. 







