HGST - Wikipedia






















 






HGST

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"Hitachi Global Storage Technologies" redirects here. It is not to be confused with Hitachi Data Systems.





This article relies too much on references to primary sources. Please improve this by adding secondary or tertiary sources. (February 2013) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)



HGST, Inc.





