hgst inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Hardware
Sub-Industry: Computer Hardware & Storage
HGST, Inc. manufactures and sells computer storage devices. The Company provides products such as external drives, internal drives, hard disks, and solid state drives for computer and mobile. HGST serves customers globally.




