 Home Page › Careers Center Careers Center
HGST is a leader in data storage, unlocking greater potential by helping the world harness the power of data. Building on its world-class reputation, HGST’s smarter storage solutions are everywhere, touching lives and enabling possibilities for the enterprise, cloud computing, and sophisticated infrastructures in healthcare, energy, finance and government.
 
.



Enable possibilities through data. Join one of Western Digital’s family of brands and help shape the future!Search WD Jobs
Search HGST Jobs
Search SanDisk Jobs


Are you ready for extraordinary? 

With the growing volume of data created by cloud services, virtualization, social networks, video and mobile platforms, advances in data storage have never been more critical. HGST is setting the pace for innovation in this evolving industry to help the world harness the power of data. Join our team to develop industry-leading storage solutions for the world’s most sophisticated technology companies and transform the world’s connection to information.

You + HGST = #HGSTBetterTogether

HGST is committed to working with and providing reasonable accommodation to applicants with physical and mental disabilities. Learn more


HGST participates in the E-Verify program in the US. For more information click here.

Este empleador participa in E-Verify.

Equal Employment Opprtunity

HGST is an Equal Opportunity Employer that is committed to inclusion and diversity. We also take affirmative action to offer employment and advancement opportunities to all applicants, including minorities, women, protected veterans, individuals with disabilities, and any other person protected by federal, state or local law. If you’d like more information about your EEO rights as an applicant, please click here.


China
HGST China is home to around 12,000 employees achieving successes in high-tech manufacturing, advanced laboratories and service and support. Join our world-class teams located in Shenzen, Beijing and Shanghai. 

Explore

India
HGST India is home to a world-class SSD team. Located in Bangalore and Pune we are on the lookout for people who redefine the next generation high speed memory architecture.

Explore

Japan
At HGST we have an innovative and high performance culture that promotes goal alignment, agility and collaboration. HGST is a great place to thrive and grow your career!

Explore

Malaysia
HGST is home to two of Malaysia’s main engineering and hi-tech hubs. Join our SSD manufacturing and research and development teams!

Explore

Philippines
HGST Philippines, Laguna, is home to over 11,000 employees transforming our global digital storage business. Join our teams to raise the standards for speed and efficiency!

Explore

Singapore
Building on the promise of data, HGST’s Singapore manufacturing and operations centers leverage a diverse multi-cultural workforce to achieve excellence. Join our diverse team!

Explore

Taiwan
HGST Taiwan plays a vital role in the worldwide success of the company and is home to two HGST sites: our SSD R&D center located in Hsinchu, the silicon village of north Taiwan and our Sales office in the country’s capital, Taipei city. Join our global teams!

Explore

Thailand
Trusted and awarded by local and international organizations HGST Thailand promotes a “Happy Workplace” and encourages creative thinking, collaboration, and teamwork. Join our winning team!

Explore

United States
The US is home to HGST's corporate headquarters in San Jose, California with locations throughout the US. At HGST we're transforming the world’s connection to information. Together, we’re solving tomorrow’s challenges today and creating new opportunities for our people. Become a part of tomorrow's solutions, join HGST!

